{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4a548534d6","title":"关于夏跳战役后行动问题的报告","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0b810241a9","index":0,"year":1935,"month":8,"day":20,"articleId":"4a548534d6"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji7-2","name":"毛泽东全集第7卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji7-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji7-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d7614f1844","type":"paragraph","text":"关于夏跳战役后行动问题的报告！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"4a548534d6"},{"id":"12e2860bdc","type":"paragraph","text":"（1935年8月20日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"4a548534d6"},{"id":"f0a598e652","type":"paragraph","text":"我们的行动方向，一是向东（陕西），一是向西（青海、新疆）。红军主力应向东，向陕、甘边界发展，不应向黄河以西。目前我们的根据地应以兆河流域为基础，将来向东发展，后方移至甘肃东北与陕西交界地区。向东还是向西是一个关键问题，应采取积极向东发展的方针。夏兆战役应采取由包座至眠州的路线，可集中三个军，甚至全部集中走这条路线。左路军应向右路军靠拢。阿坝要迅速打一下。应坚持向东打，不应以一些困难转而向西","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"4a548534d6"},{"id":"7e11f30fd3","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]1935年8月20日，中共中央政治局在毛儿盖召开会议，毛泽东在会议上作关于夏跳战役后行动问题的报告。这是报告的一部分。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"4a548534d6"}],"page":{"id":"0bc0ec22cd","publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"4a548534d6","start":215,"end":215}}}},"__N_SSG":true}